race.description: Fowler Civil Contracting Super Mdn Plate
race.comment: VILLA CASTINA (10) followed a midfield finish behind Attica in the Listed Dulcify with a disappointing performance over 1500m at Muswellbrook last start as $1.50 favourite. May have been a bit flat after the good run in stakes company. Back up to the mile and looks the testing material. PIERRO LAD (6) warmed to the task late to just miss last time out over 1400m at Kembla. Steps out for only the fourth time and is crying out for 1600m. Clearly the biggest danger. LET'S BE HONEST (8) gets back in her races but finds the line with gusto. Can race a bit closer from a better gate today - one to watch for late in the piece. SOLID (7) comes here second-up. Safely accounted for at each of his three runs to date. Was not a factor last start at Rosehill when fifth over 1400m. Finds a suitable race and worth including.
